title: FLT - Cool World Cracktro
info:
The cracktro sported a huge FLT logo in the middle with little scrollies at the top and bottom.  There was a basic 3-level parralax starfield in the back and that music was playing all the while.

Not sure if it was Fairlight or some other knock-off.. I never could rip the song out or even find who did the song.
